channel.title: 317 Mac Compatible?
channel.description:
Hello. I'm currently in the process in finding a good 317 source. But, I have many people going to be playing the server, but they have macs. I also have a Mac. So I was wondering which source would be Mac compatible so I could code and play off of it.
If anyone can link me to a 317 source that is, indeed Mac compatible. It would be very helpful.
Thank you for your time.

item.title: 317 Mac Compatible?
item.dc:creator: @Shadow77116 Shadow77116
item.description:
@Shadow77116 wrote:

RiiPiiNFtW:

All you need is System.getProperties("user.home");

I will try that. Thank you.
